data.description: Nicely maintained and renovated home on a large lot featuring numerous updates. New windows and newly painted exterior.  The exterior has brick features and is quietly situated on a dead end street with no cross traffic.  The home boasts plenty of natural light with high ceilings in the main living area. Nicely sized bedrooms are all on the left side of the house and the efficient layout has little wasted space.  Recent improvements include the new roof, flooring, appliances, and gutters.  The back patio offers a private outdoor space, perfect for enjoying the natural surroundings and entertaining guests.  Easy location is minutes to I-485 and Route 74.
